[band playing "Over There"]

1105
01:34:24,174 --> 01:34:31,025
<i>It's a long way to Tipperary,
it's a long way to go.</i>

1106
01:34:31,060 --> 01:34:38,221
<i>It's a long way to Tipperary, 
to the sweetest girl I know...</i>

1107
01:34:45,645 --> 01:34:51,820
<i>Goodbye Broadway, hello, France.
We're ten million strong.</i>

1108
01:34:51,855 --> 01:34:55,404
<i>We're gonna kick the Kaiser
in his pants,</i>

1109
01:34:55,439 --> 01:34:59,129
<i>and it isn't gonna take us,
isn't gonna take us,</i>

1110
01:34:59,164 --> 01:35:02,746
<i>isn't gonna take us long.</i>

1111
01:35:03,304 --> 01:35:06,552
[band playing "Yankee Doodle"]

1112
01:35:09,425 --> 01:35:16,648
<i>There are smiles that make us happy,
there are smiles that make us blue;</i>

1113
01:35:16,648 --> 01:35:23,849
<i>there are smiles that steal away the teardrops 
as the sunbeams steal away the dew.</i>

1114
01:35:24,860 --> 01:35:31,018
[band playing "Mademoiselle from Armentires"] 

1115
01:35:32,635 --> 01:35:38,956
