<i>Oui, oui, oui.</i>

1117
01:35:39,939 --> 01:35:46,555
<i>When you say "Oui, oui," la, la.
It just means you and me, Papa.</i>

1118
01:35:46,555 --> 01:35:49,716
<i>Oh, Frenchie, oh Frenchie...</i>

1119
01:35:55,553 --> 01:36:02,222
<i>Pack up your troubles in your old kit-bag 
and smile, smile, smile.</i>

1120
01:36:02,222 --> 01:36:09,113
<i>While you've a lucifer to light your fag,
smile, boys, that's the style.</i>

1121
01:36:09,113 --> 01:36:15,789
<i>What's the use of worrying,
it never was worth while,</i>

1122
